### --------------------------------------------------
### 步骤8: 验证数据导入结果
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://es.ai.k8s:80/factory_sensors,app_logs,user_orders/_stats/docs
Accept: */*

### --------------------------------------------------
### 步骤9: 查看各索引Mapping（供DSL生成参考）
### --------------------------------------------------
###
GET http://es.ai.k8s:80/factory_sensors/_mapping
Accept: */*

###
GET http://es.ai.k8s:80/app_logs/_mapping
Accept: */*

